Federal Register: 170. Monuron (CAS No. 000150-68-5) (FIFRA SR) (Ref. 8). The measured aquatic toxicity data for monuron include a 1.5-hour EC sub 50 of 90 ppb and a 10-day EC sub 50 of 100 ppb for marine algae. EPA believes that there is sufficient evidence for listing monuron on EPCRA section 313 pursuant to EPCRA section 313(d)(2)(C) based on the environmental toxicity data for this chemical.
